579
00:26:52,140 --> 00:26:53,980
Bring her to the outer courtyard.

580
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:56,140
Just don't let Lady Xu find out.

581
00:26:56,340 --> 00:26:57,180
You...

582
00:26:57,860 --> 00:26:58,820
I'm going now.

583
00:27:13,740 --> 00:27:14,820
Where

584
00:27:14,820 --> 00:27:16,260
