585
00:27:17,100 --> 00:27:17,940
My Lady.

586
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:20,180
My Lady.

587
00:27:20,340 --> 00:27:21,820
The guest list is ready.

588
00:27:21,820 --> 00:27:23,020
No need to consult Lady Zhu.

589
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,860
My Lady.

590
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:31,120
Here are ritual records
of birthday banquets in Yujun,

591
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,880
family genealogy, guest list records,

592
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:35,300
and family gathering records.

593
00:27:35,370 --> 00:27:36,620
They're all for your reference.

594
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,020
Thank you.

595
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:40,180
Can I take these back with me?

596
00:27:40,180 --> 00:27:42,580
Of course.
But there's no need to carry them.

597
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:44,500
The Lord said you could use the study.

598
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:45,860
If you need any books or records,

599
00:27:45,860 --> 00:27:46,940
just ask me.

600
00:27:47,820 --> 00:27:49,380
The Lord prepared these?

601
00:27:50,180 --> 00:27:51,020
Yes.

602
00:27:53,620 --> 00:27:55,460
(Guest List)

603
00:27:58,380 --> 00:28:00,540
What does the Lord mean?

604
00:28:01,740 --> 00:28:04,180
Maybe he's afraid I'll ruin the banquet

605
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,380
and embarrass him.

606
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:06,820
Or maybe he genuinely

607
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:08,580
cares about you.

608
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:18,260
Chuyu.

609
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,700
Let me look.

610
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:21,540
Aunt,

611
00:28:21,980 --> 00:28:23,500
please save me.

612
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:24,980
Come on, get up.

613
00:28:26,180 --> 00:28:27,420
What happened to your face?

614
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:28,740
Get up now.

615
00:28:30,740 --> 00:28:32,900
They accused me of being indecent
with another man

616
00:28:33,300 --> 00:28:35,580
