squandered my dowry

617
00:28:35,740 --> 00:28:37,940
and wanted more money from you.

618
00:28:38,580 --> 00:28:39,420
Aunt,

619
00:28:39,580 --> 00:28:41,460
the marriage Lady Xu arranged for me

620
00:28:41,460 --> 00:28:43,220
has put me in great misery.

621
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:46,020
My life hasn't been easy either.

622
00:28:46,780 --> 00:28:48,300
If it weren't for Lady Qiao,

623
00:28:48,340 --> 00:28:49,980
you would've had everything you wanted.

624
00:28:50,580 --> 00:28:51,420
It looks like

625
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:53,100
to make this work,

626
00:28:53,540 --> 00:28:55,260
we need Lady Qiao to slip up

627
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:57,100
so you can have the upper hand.

628
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:59,420
Mother supports her now.

629
00:28:59,420 --> 00:29:00,820
What can I do?

630
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,660
There

631
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:04,780
might be a way,

632
00:29:05,700 --> 00:29:07,260
but it depends on you.

633
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:19,180
(Granary)

634
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:20,100
Greetings, Mr. Wei.

635
00:29:20,100 --> 00:29:21,940
Anything unusual in the granary today?

636
00:29:22,460 --> 00:29:23,340
All is as usual.

637
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:24,460
Please rest assured.

638
00:29:32,340 --> 00:29:33,780
(Granary)

639
00:29:42,020 --> 00:29:43,400
Ehuang, it's done.

640
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:45,780
A grand birthday celebration

641
00:29:46,810 --> 00:29:48,260
needs to be livelier.

642
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:12,220
I heard

643
00:30:12,220 --> 00:30:13,900
Lady Yulou is gifted in music.

644
00:30:14,340 --> 00:30:15,220
Would I

645
00:30:15,500 --> 00:30:16,820
be lucky enough

646
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:18,740
to enjoy a performance today?

647
00:30:19,700 --> 00:30:21,020
The Lord of Wei has heard me sing.

648
00:30:21,370 --> 00:30:22,410
You may ask him.

649
00:30:23,020 --> 00:30:23,860
Shiyuan,

650
00:30:24,450 --> 00:30:25,820
Lady Yulou is noble now.

651
00:30:26,590 --> 00:30:28,740
She's no longer someone

652
00:30:29,430 --> 00:30:31,220
you can joke with like before.

653
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:34,180
I only hope

654
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:35,740
her singing can entertain you

655
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:38,100
on this special day.

656
00:30:38,700 --> 00:30:39,780
How do you plan

657
00:30:40,260 --> 00:30:42,260
to entertain me yourself?

