00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:47,020
Shiyuan,

659
00:30:47,660 --> 00:30:49,020
why not perform a sword dance?

660
00:30:49,660 --> 00:30:51,300
I can sing along.

661
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,220
What do you think?

662
00:30:56,660 --> 00:30:57,740
That'll be wonderful.

663
00:30:57,740 --> 00:30:59,020
It'll be great.

664
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,670
Sounds good.

665
00:31:19,090 --> 00:31:21,530
♪The graceful grass♪

666
00:31:22,710 --> 00:31:25,560
♪Stands alone yet captivating♪

667
00:31:26,250 --> 00:31:28,920
♪My longing for it♪

668
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:32,650
♪Twists into the night♪

669
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:36,770
♪The graceful grass♪

670
00:31:36,770 --> 00:31:39,870
♪Carries my distant yearning♪

671
00:31:39,870 --> 00:31:43,150
♪My honest husband♪

672
00:31:43,380 --> 00:31:47,750
♪Truly worries me♪

673
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,420
Bravo!

674
00:31:52,420 --> 00:31:53,580
How beautiful!

675
00:31:53,580 --> 00:31:54,420
Beautiful!

676
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:56,100
Mr. Wei is truly charming.

677
00:31:56,100 --> 00:31:57,960
You're hiding such talent.

678
00:31:57,970 --> 00:31:59,390
If you were on the battlefield,

679
00:31:59,390 --> 00:32:00,860
you'd be a mighty warrior for sure.

680
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:03,180
Indeed.

681
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:08,420
Your voice is like that of a goddess.

682
00:32:08,500 --> 00:32:09,820
Thank you, Great-aunt.

683
00:32:10,260 --> 00:32:11,100
Grandmother,

684
00:32:11,460 --> 00:32:12,580
may you

685
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:14,640
live long with endless blessings

686
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,060
and everlasting health

687
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,340
and peace.

688
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:21,420
Mother, you must be
in high spirits today.

689
00:32:21,730 --> 00:32:22,980
Shiyuan performed.

690
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:25,740
Lady Qiao gave a thoughtful gift.

691
00:32:26,420 --> 00:32:27,700
I heard Yanzhou

692
00:32:27,920 --> 00:32:30,300
also sent a generous gift.

693
00:32:31,190 --> 00:32:32,820
Grandmother has seen it.

694
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:35,700
Yanzhou sent winter wheat seeds.

695
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,380
Just seeds?

696
00:32:38,390 --> 00:32:40,940
Winter wheat is the foundation
of Yanzhou's prosperity.

697
00:32:41,290 --> 00:32:42,900
Giving this

698
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:44,330
shows great sincerity.

699
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:47,210
It's the best birthday gift
I could receive.

700
00:32:48,140 --> 00:32:49,940
It's just winter wheat.

701
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:51,480
Is it really that special?

702
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:56,460
You didn't seem interested

703
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:58,500
in this before.

704
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:02,220
Zhonglin, what are you doing?

705
00:33:02,740 --> 00:33:03,580
I...

706
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:05,100
Want to use the restroom?

707
00:33:05,300 --> 00:33:06,260
Go on then.

708
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,300
This child...

709
00:33:09,300 --> 00:33:11,900
Mother, I mean no offense.

710
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:13,700
I'm just curious.

711
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,740
Since we're all here,

712
00:33:15,740 --> 00:33:16,700
why not have Lady Qiao

713
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:18,700
bring out the seeds

714
00:33:18,700 --> 00:33:20,580
for everyone to see?

715
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:21,420
Right?

716
00:33:21,580 --> 00:33:23,020
- Yes.
- Great.

717
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:24,780
Let's see them.

718
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,460
We want to see
what winter wheat is like.

719
00:33:28,340 --> 00:33:29,180
Grandmother.

720
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,020
Mother.

721
00:33:30,430 --> 00:33:32,260
These are the wheat seeds from Yanzhou.

722
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:34,220
Please have a look.

723
00:33:34,780 --> 00:33:36,830
This winter wheat

724
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:38,180
is an improved strain.

725
00:33:38,290 --> 00:33:39,720
It's planted in the autumn equinox

726
00:33:39,750 --> 00:33:41,000
and harvested in the fifth month

727
00:33:41,010 --> 00:33:42,260
of the next year.

728
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:45,020
It's perfect for easing food shortages
in early summer.

729
00:33:45,420 --> 00:33:46,700
But winter wheat

730
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,260
has always been exclusive to Yanzhou.

731
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:51,180
Yanzhou produces and sells them,

732
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:52,740
but it never gives away seeds.

733
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:54,340
This time,

734
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:56,220
on Grandmother's birthday,

735
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:57,460
Yanzhou shares them

736
00:33:58,020 --> 00:33:58,980
in hopes

737
00:33:59,260 --> 00:34:00,580
of standing together with Wei

738
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:01,900
through thick and thin.

739
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:05,260
What's that smell?

740
00:34:05,740 --> 00:34:06,580
Could it

741
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:07,940
be mold?

742
00:34:08,860 --> 00:34:09,700
Yes.

743
00:34:10,300 --> 00:34:11,660
How dare you!

744
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:14,420
I want to ask you today.

745
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:16,060
What exactly is your family up to?

746
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,460
Fourteen years ago,

747
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:18,660
you broke your word

748
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:20,020
on the battlefield

749
00:34:20,180 --> 00:34:22,620
and caused enough misery to our family.

750
00:34:22,780 --> 00:34:24,060
How dare you present

751
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:25,540
these rotten seeds as a gift?

752
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:26,620
Take them away!

753
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,300
Mother,

754
00:34:30,740 --> 00:34:32,100
I personally inspected

755
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:34,980
these seeds.

756
00:34:36,030 --> 00:34:38,700
Every single one was carefully selected.

757
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:41,620
This concerns an alliance
between our families

758
00:34:41,820 --> 00:34:43,420
and the lives of our people.

759
00:34:43,690 --> 00:34:45,310
The Qiao Clan would never

760
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:47,060
treat it lightly.

761
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:49,900
From what I see,

762
00:34:50,180 --> 00:34:51,700
each grain is full and intact.

763
00:34:53,140 --> 00:34:54,100
They're not rotten.

764
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:00,860
Though the seeds

765
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,140
aren't rotten,

766
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:04,180
they're floating.

767
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,330
They're cooked!

768
00:35:07,330 --> 00:35:08,540
Cooked!

769
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,900
They're cooked!

770
00:35:09,900 --> 00:35:11,060
How could they be cooked?

771
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:12,300
They're truly cooked.

772
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:13,340
Cooked seeds.

773
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:17,020
How can cooked seeds be planted?

774
00:35:17,020 --> 00:35:18,300
Let me see.

775
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:24,580
It's hard to tell if they're raw seeds.

776
00:35:25,250 --> 00:35:27,540
If the people plant them

777
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,130
and they don't sprout,

778
00:35:29,940 --> 00:35:31,630
they'll blame themselves

779
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:33,120
for not tending the fields properly.

780
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:35,060
Then they'll miss the planting season,

781
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,620
and the famine will be even worse
than this year.

782
00:35:38,980 --> 00:35:40,500
People live on food.

783
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:42,660
Everyone, they must hate us deeply.

784
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,660
Exactly.

785
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:45,060
What were they thinking?

786
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:46,950
The seeds that won't grow.

787
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:48,140
What a malicious scheme.

788
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:50,620
It looks like Yanzhou's seeds are here

789
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,580
to cause havoc.

790
00:35:52,670 --> 00:35:54,120
We demand an explanation today.

791
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,070
What's going on?

792
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,620
The seeds are the foundation of a state.

793
00:35:56,620 --> 00:35:57,520
We need an explanation.

794
00:35:57,530 --> 00:35:59,280
Everyone says
Yanzhou's seeds are the best.

795
00:35:59,380 --> 00:36:01,300
If they send us duds,

796
00:36:02,020 --> 00:36:03,940
the farmers will suffer.

797
00:36:04,700 --> 00:36:07,060
If the seeds are steamed and dried,

798
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:08,820
it'll be hard to tell if they're cooked

799
00:36:09,100 --> 00:36:10,660
without careful examination.

800
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:12,350
We can test them

801
00:36:13,050 --> 00:36:14,000
to find out.

802
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:16,860
Look. Some are floating.

803
00:36:16,860 --> 00:36:17,820
Look, look.

804
00:36:18,340 --> 00:36:19,420
They're cooked.

805
00:36:19,770 --> 00:36:20,660
That's right.

806
00:36:20,750 --> 00:36:21,700
They're all cooked.

807
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,580
The seeds are all cooked.

808
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:26,020
That can't be.

809
00:36:26,240 --> 00:36:27,100
My Lady,

810
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:28,300
I swear I didn't know.

811
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,780
Grandmother.

812
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:31,420
Everyone.

813
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:33,180
My uncle may be foolish,

814
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,940
but this is serious.

815
00:36:36,460 --> 00:36:38,020
He would never risk

816
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:40,340
the lives of Wei's people.

817
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:42,060
There must be a misunderstanding.

818
00:36:42,180 --> 00:36:43,060
A misunderstanding?

819
00:36:44,540 --> 00:36:46,020
Good thing there's no war now.

820
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,700
Grain is extremely important in wars.

821
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:50,380
How would we feed the soldiers

822
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:51,780
and the people without grain?

823
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:53,740
The Qiao Clan

824
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:55,300
- is so vile.
- Indeed.

825
00:36:55,320 --> 00:36:56,630
There will be famine every year.

826
00:36:56,640 --> 00:36:58,660
My Lady, what should we do?

827
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:00,340
Shall I go beg the Lord?

828
00:37:01,540 --> 00:37:03,160
He might not help us.

829
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:05,790
It's a plot against our people.

830
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,940
We must get to the bottom of this today.

831
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:09,100
We demand an explanation.

832
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:10,220
We need an answer.

833
00:37:10,660 --> 00:37:12,900
The Lady has always been cautious here

834
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:14,900
just like me.

835
00:37:15,780 --> 00:37:18,180
How can you gang up on a woman?

836
00:37:19,100 --> 00:37:20,980
How can a lady of inner chambers

837
00:37:21,940 --> 00:37:23,900
get involved

838
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:25,500
in political affairs?

839
00:37:26,380 --> 00:37:27,460
In my opinion,

840
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,940
it was Qiao Yue who did this.

841
00:37:31,380 --> 00:37:32,220
Grandmother,

842
00:37:33,100 --> 00:37:36,100
perhaps someone plotted to frame us.

843
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:38,540
Please look into it fairly.

844
00:37:39,100 --> 00:37:40,060
Look into it?

845
00:37:40,220 --> 00:37:42,500
The truth is right before us.
Stop trying to deny it.

846
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:44,500
They might not be seeds from Yanzhou.

847
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:46,300
They're definitely from Yanzhou.

848
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:48,140
- Stop denying it.
- Exactly.

849
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:50,140
Yanzhou's envoy presented them.

850
00:37:50,340 --> 00:37:51,420
They must be from Yanzhou.

851
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:52,580
How wicked.

852
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:54,860
You try to use steamed seeds
to fool the people.

853
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:56,220
What are you up to?

854
00:37:56,220 --> 00:37:57,800
This is Grandmother's birthday banquet,

855
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:58,820
not a place for shouting.

856
00:37:58,880 --> 00:37:59,620
Silence!

857
00:38:08,220 --> 00:38:09,500
Shao, they're all cooked.

858
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:10,500
I already know.

859
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:12,060
In that case,

860
00:38:12,060 --> 00:38:13,540
punish the Lady now.

861
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:27,380
At Grandmother's birthday banquet,

862
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:29,240
what a surprise to see a mystery

863
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:31,100
instead of a puppet show.

864
00:38:32,580 --> 00:38:33,500
Clearly,

865
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:37,100
someone wanted to disgrace our family.

866
00:38:37,410 --> 00:38:38,380
What mystery?

867
00:38:38,670 --> 00:38:40,820
Lady Qiao clearly plotted this.

868
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:41,900
With bad seeds,

